# Weather Agent

AI-powered Weather Agent built using Python, [LangChain](https://python.langchain.com?utm_source=chatgpt.com), and [AWS Bedrock](https://aws.amazon.com/bedrock/?utm_source=chatgpt.com).
The agent uses an LLM hosted on AWS Bedrock to intelligently decide when to call a weather tool and provide concise weather summaries.

---

# Features

* AI Agent using LangChain
* AWS Bedrock integration
* Amazon Nova Micro model
* Real-time weather data
* Open-Meteo API integration
* Tool calling with LangChain
* Structured weather responses

---

# Architecture

```text
User
  ↓
LangChain Agent
  ↓
AWS Bedrock (Nova Micro)
  ↓
Weather Tool (Python Function)
  ↓
Open-Meteo API
  ↓
Weather Data
  ↓
LLM formats final response
```

